LanguageData.WNA_SeedAnima.label: anima tree seed
LanguageData.WNA_SeedAnima.description: An egg-like soft jelly ball placed on a small maintaining plate. When planted at somewhere available, this ball of biomass will activate and grow into an anima tree. WNA - Whelingnorther Alliance
